# Marketing transitions

Before changing Talent/Work card clicks or viewer morph behavior, read **`docs/marketing/transitions/transition.md`**.

Run matrix QA after any change:

```bash
node scripts/marketing/run-transition-matrix-qc.mjs --url=https://reels.friendsandfamily.tv
```

Non-negotiable: one hero layer during morph, freeze source rect at click, hide `[data-marketing-featured-media-target]` until morph completes, no scroll during morph.
